      <title>特朗普放弃与俄罗斯谈判结束乌克兰战争，油价维持跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普与俄罗斯总统普京同意就结束乌克兰战争进行谈判，引发市场猜测俄罗斯供应风险可能缓解，油价因此出现两个多月来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 23:35:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
